          <article class="s-section" id="components-stat">
            <header class="s-section-head">
              <span class="s-section-num">3.5</span>
              <h3>Stat block — <code>.stat-block</code></h3>
            </header>
            <p>Vertical accent bar + display-weight declarative statement. Maximum two per article. Never for opinions — only verifiable claims or theological declarations.</p>
            <div class="s-demo-frame">
              <div class="s-demo-label">Live · <code>.stat-block</code></div>
              <div class="stat-block">
                <div class="stat-block-bar"></div>
