          <!-- CLOSING -->
          <article class="s-section" id="components-closing">
            <header class="s-section-head">
              <span class="s-section-num">3.6</span>
              <h3>Closing — <code>.closing</code></h3>
            </header>
            <p>The essay's final beat. A short declarative line, centered, bordered top and bottom with content-weight rules. One per essay, at the end. Not a CTA. Not a summary. The last sentence that earns the read.</p>
            <div class="s-demo-frame">
              <div class="s-demo-label">Live · <code>.closing</code></div>
