          <!-- ISSUE HEAD -->
          <article class="s-section" id="components-issuehead">
            <header class="s-section-head">
              <span class="s-section-num">3.8</span>
              <h3>Issue head — <code>.issue-head</code></h3>
            </header>
            <p>Masthead of the editorial issue. Sits directly under the site chrome on the homepage. Carries the issue number, week stamp, and a "latest" standfirst that deep-links to the current essay. The reader knows which edition they landed on before they read a word.</p>
            <p class="s-note"><strong>Rules.</strong> Issue number increments only with a new lead essay. Week stamp is always the publication week, not the current week. The standfirst block is the <em>only</em> place an essay link coexists with editorial metadata above the archive.</p>
