            <p>The author block. Split main / side layout — name on one side at display scale, short bio + two actions on the other. Never more than two actions. Primary action links to the full about page; secondary anchors the subscribe manifesto.</p>
            <p class="s-note"><strong>Hard rules.</strong> One identity hero per site. Never on article pages. Never duplicated on social. The name is <em>always</em> "Dexter Jakes" — no first-name-only, no handle-as-name. The corner eyebrow ("The Writer → 01") maps to issue numbering.</p>
