          <!-- ISSUE NEXT -->
          <article class="s-section" id="components-issuenext">
            <header class="s-section-head">
              <span class="s-section-num">3.13</span>
              <h3>Issue next — <code>.issue-next</code></h3>
            </header>
            <p>The teaser strip. A single-line announcement for the next essay in the queue — title, lane, estimated drop date, read time, and a "notify me" affordance that anchors back to the subscribe manifesto. Sits between the archive and the subscribe block. Disappears the moment the next essay publishes.</p>
